 6.8 of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "blandfordCP"

\end_inset

 should be 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{F}=\lim_{T\rightarrow\infty}\frac{1}{T}\int_{-T/2}^{T/2}F\left(y\left(t\right)\right)dt$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

]].
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Correspondingly, we can blur the distinction between the random process
 and speciﬁc realizations of it
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

